{"tid":2115192,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"南洋商業銀行當分行員工係地底泥？","createTime":"2020-07-19T10:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T05:52:21.000Z","uid":239263,"like":70,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"358d15c3a9d2a56d46134c06a0451374275e335e","tid":2115192,"uid":239263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"第一，想當日第一波爆發，都有安排員工分A B team返工，現在就得返4:00關門，疫情嚴重左，但就唔安排work from home<br />\n<br />\n第二，前線員工對外接觸客人機會好多，染疫機會都更高，相反其他部門染疫機會較低但就有安排A B team上班，是否前線員工生命較為低賤<br />\n<br />\n第三，以往前線分A B Team上班仍能維持有限度服務，與此同時又可以減低前線員工染疫風險，講緊係當時每日十幾單確診都有A B team措施，但現在每日過百單確診反而無A B team措施，南洋高層撫心自問講唔講得通，口講以人為本，實際就只有顧客重要，前線員工就人命如糞土，提早就一小時關門就心安理得當施捨狗"},{"pid":"a092890860f85f3506bb7b86242a3bcfde3b7bc1","tid":2115192,"uid":166733,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"唔少公司back office都冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b543cee8aeadd705ca824a0b7bc8059d055ccdf","tid":2115192,"uid":239263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"57cc5a0cc0edfb1f9cf677a51e605def95f71f8b","tid":2115192,"uid":239263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:39:32.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f976f332d418a93d2260c2d7e9857b2c9e3263e4","tid":2115192,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"南洋究極奶共公司辭咗佢啦<br />\n利申仲係中銀子公司嗰陣老母喺呢間嘢做 一賣盤就閃人"},{"pid":"e86efb51e88b924e3998f21f3525e0fc2d1dfced","tid":2115192,"uid":252000,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"唔好話淨係分行同事啦，根本成間公司個管理層就有問題，做野仲慢過政府，疫情第三波內部BO至FO都冇WFH<br />\n<br />\n有個department到依家都冇split team，淨係識迫人請假，係強迫！！！我想講輪住請假係冇用嫁！只要一日唔split team，只要有一條友中左，只要佢個日接觸過其他同事，其他同事又繼續輪住返，咁咪姐係成個department出事！依家出面度度都WFH啦！間銀行做到咁大規模都要迫人請假！<br />\n<br />\n講白啲split team係為公司運作著想，WFH係為保障員工健康，但唔好意思呢間垃圾2樣都冇（只少我個department係咁）<br />\n<br />\nSplit team唔提供office電話要人用自己手提聽係咩玩法？WFH又冇手提電腦，呢間公司啲管理層落後到爆，完全唔知出面世界！從來唔會聽員工意見！聽到唔聽！"},{"pid":"c3745376665e31e630d21852a5fb131c0fa711fd","tid":2115192,"uid":52540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc17528ad99909717188fbd07b1bd1d0acb1798","tid":2115192,"uid":347237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"中資管理係咁架"},{"pid":"5046c64296c880a00dcf802340787a1f473ad155","tid":2115192,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"5ad6abcd57bef9df0560e0d37545cfb7694b39e7","tid":2115192,"uid":96662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:25:34.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c4b81f99befd28e5a378e06631526a59acd7cf06","tid":2115192,"uid":70515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:35:29.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cbbf2c02d274bceffc9bf8540d7b9f24aaafb0","tid":2115192,"uid":231110,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:45:03.000Z","msg":"前線員工WFH係咩玩法？<br />\n在家對客？"},{"pid":"4140550426857d95329ff7208762478d81539e54","tid":2115192,"uid":252000,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"67cbbf2c02d274bceffc9bf8540d7b9f24aaafb0","tid":2115192,"uid":231110,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:45:03.000Z","msg":"前線員工WFH係咩玩法？<br />\n在家對客？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"其實前線唔係淨係得分行同事(Retail)，仲有SME，Corporate Banking，雖然唔會坐分行，但一樣係FO"},{"pid":"b16e01772879df49f2f9f8b8c7606c5d45441988","tid":2115192,"uid":87493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:04:35.000Z","msg":"有四點關門咩？"},{"pid":"cff9d4f0315a971ac023ee45d562f0ae5f71cf15","tid":2115192,"uid":252000,"like":